<worksheet label="ws-act-poly-infty-limit">
  <activity xml:id="act-poly-infty-limit">
    <statement>
      <p>
			Complete the <xref ref="T-familiar-infty-limits">Table</xref> by entering
		    <q><m>\infty</m>,</q><q><m>-\infty</m>,</q><q><m>0</m>,</q> or <q>no limit</q>
		    to identify how the function behaves as either <m>x</m> increases or decreases without bound.
		    As much as possible, work to decide the behavior <em>without</em> using a graphing utility.
		</p>
